nt-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>Earlier it was not possible to change the Facebook page name, not at all. Now, it is quite easy. But, Facebook will have to approve it first. Here are a few topics I\u2019ll be covering in this blog to help you change Facebook Page name easily.<\/p><h2><b>What is a Facebook Page?<\/b><\/h2><div>\u00a0<\/div><div>Facebook pages are a way to create a personal website for yourself or a group of people. They&#8217;re free, and you can create as many pages as you need. You can post anything on your page, and people can Like, Comment, and Share your posts. Facebook pages are great for sharing information with a large audience, promoting your business or organization, and building relationships.<\/div><div>\u00a0<\/div><h3><b>How Do I Change My Page Name On Facebook In 2024?<\/b><\/h3><p>To change the Facebook page name, you must be the admin of that page.; then you can request to change your page name.<\/p><p><strong>It\u2019s A Very Simple Process And Involves The Following Steps:<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\"><b>1)<\/b><\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\"> Go to Facebook and login as an admin of the Facebook page you wish to change<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c70150 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3c70150\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.18.0 - 20-12-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-18628\" alt=\"Change Facebook Page Name\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2-1.jpg 560w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2-1-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac2099f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac2099f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2) Click on\u00a0<strong>About<\/strong>\u00a0on the left side of the page<\/p><p>3) Click on\u00a0<strong>Page info<\/strong><\/p><p>4) Click on\u00a0<strong>Name<\/strong>\u00a0\u2192<strong>\u00a0Edit<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c6d350 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9c6d350\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/3-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-18629\" alt=\"Change Facebook Page Name\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/3-1.jpg 560w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/3-1-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7ecc8f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a7ecc8f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>5) Enter a\u00a0<strong>new name page<\/strong>\u00a0\u2192\u00a0<strong>continue<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-480324c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"480324c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-18630\" alt=\"new name page\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/4.jpg 560w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/4-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7932fa4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7932fa4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>6) Review your request \u2192 Request changeCaution:<\/p><p>\u00a0Be sure and accurate for the name you changed because this cannot be undone.<\/p><p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-advertising\/\">How To Start Advertising on Facebook<\/a><\/p><h3>Why Can\u2019t I Change My Page Name On Facebook?<\/h3><p>Here are the reasons:<\/p><p><b>1)<\/b> Your page has too many likes; more than 200 likes.<\/p><p><b>2)<\/b> You or another admin changed the page name less than seven days ago.<\/p><p><b>3)<\/b> You must have to break Facebook rules or use the wrong tactics to get likes.<\/p><p>4) You can not change the name of a regional page if it falls into a global page.<\/p><p>5) There may be limits to your page like<\/p><ul><li>Your page has misleading content<\/li><li>Your page has a misleading name<\/li><li>The admin of your page has not followed facebook policies<\/li><\/ul><p>If none of these reasons seem to fit your situation, you can go to\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/help\/1126628984024935?helpref=hc_global_nav\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook reports<\/a>\u00a0and submit an appeal to change your page name by filling out the form to appeal.<\/p><p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/check-facebook-followers\/\">How to See Who is Following Your Facebook Page<\/a><\/p><h3>How Long Do You Have To Wait To Change Your Facebook Page Name?<\/h3><p>If you want to change your page name, then you have to wait for seven days because page name changes are permitted once in seven days. The new page name may take approx 3-4 days for reviews, so start as early as possible to make sure that your new name launched is aligned.<\/p><p><strong>Also Learn:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-post-ideas\/\">Actionable Facebook Post Ideas<\/a><\/p><h4>Conclusion<\/h4><p>Once it is approved, you cannot change the name again for another seven days and till then Facebook will let your page fans know that you have updated your Facebook page name.<\/p><p><strong>Also Check<\/strong>:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-page-promotion\/\">How To Promote A Facebook Business Page?<\/a><\/p><p>If you still face any issues regarding the Facebook page, you may\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/contact\/\">contact us<\/a>\u00a0by commenting below or emailing us. We are ready to serve you always!<\/p><p>In conclusion, hiring RankON Technologies for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.